1. *Živ* je bio umoran nakon dugog putovanja. (He was tired after the long journey.)
2. Dečak je bio *živ* i radostan. (The boy was lively and joyful.)
3. Nisam znao da je još *živ*. (I didn't know he was still alive.)
4. Putnici su čekali *žive* vijesti. (The travelers were waiting for news.)
5. Ona se borila da bi ostala *živa*. (She fought to stay alive.)
6. U njegovim očima bila je velika *živost*. (In his eyes there was great liveliness.)